name: AQST Ambassador Token
description: A token of peace and prosperity throughout the universe. Sell for 1000 Tez to unlock a Galaxy for the seller and the Buyer, and a 3rd listed for public sale. Each Galaxy Produces 3 Planets, 9 Mining Operations, 27 Research Artifacts, and 81 Rare Artifacts. The Galaxy may also be burned to create a Black Hole. Created by @alexdelia for Artifact.Quest 2021.
